"11/04/2020 06:43am","77.145.167.56","0","0033619975492","Boualemazari@gmail.com","09/01/1987","Célibataire","Hôtesse - Stewart Jet Privé","1800 D","

Led a team of up to 30 team members in a multi-lingual and cultural management challenge providing industry-leading service to 600 customers. 
•	Ensured the safety of passengers onboard by verifying safety procedures including on-the-job training for crew members.
•	Part of the management team who helped the airline achieve its three-time “World’s Best Airline” award.
•	Used advanced tools to document and follow up on both customer experience and staff performance evaluation.
•	Promoted the Etihad brand by acting as an advocate for their full range of aviation products.

Delivering world class service on board the Emirates and Etihad Aircrafts, holding up to 600 customers.
•	My hard work and dedication earned me a fast track promotion to Cabin Manager and Safety and Emergency Trainer within 2 years.

	Delivered course material to a varied mix of over 1000 international employees.
•	Led over 6000 hours of classroom and practical training.
•	Practical assessment and training of new staff on world-class advanced simulators 
