Your company enjoys a well-known reputation for quality of service in the world of aviation and I would like to have the opportunity to make my first job within your dynamic team and anxious to offer customers personalized service. and of quality, of which she will be able to keep the best memories. In the long term, this attitude leads to the loyalty of these customers.

Impeccable presentation, I speak English fluently and have some notions of Chinese.
Endowed with good physical resistance, I know how to adapt to the long working days and the staggered schedules imposed by this position which generate, without a doubt, a certain fatigue in the long run that we must know how to manage.

I will be happy to have the opportunity to participate in one of your next recruitment days so that I can show you my motivations.


