English : 

Born into a Franco-British family, I am perfectly bilingual. It has served me well through my travels and my jobs internationally.
Currently employed on a private mega-yacht in the Mediterranean, I am strengthening my skills in personalized service. As Chef Stewardess I am responsible for keeping an impeccable living space and delivering a service dedicated to the smooth running of the guests' stay. I am used to handling invoices, online orders, making all kinds of purchases and supervising staff. Having travelled a lot for pleasure or for expatriation (in Canada and Australia) I know my way around booking and organizing adventures. Thanks to that, I also gained administrative experience, leaving and returning to France, then I assisted my father in all his Brexit and retirement matters. Today I am ready for a new challenge.
I think I am the ideal person for the job.
I really think I could be a strong asset for this American family, I will be able to accompany them gently in their integration of this new French life. I would love to get to know you so that I can introduce myself in person and communicate my energy and enthusiasm face to face!
